       <b><font color="#990000"><font size="+3">Evolutionary Trends in Trilobites</font></font></b> 
   <br>








     <small>This page last revised 20 July 2008</small><small> by <a href="mailto:goniagnostus@yahoo.com">S.M. Gon III</a></small><br>








             
